narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: RUSS 145 is a course meant for people who are vary serious about learning Russian. It takes a lot of work, but in my opinion, not only does it pay off, but it's really the proper way to learn this language. I would recommend the course without any reservations.
This is a fantastic course: language learning at the proper pace (or, if anything, a little slow). Take it and you'll never regret it. As long as you can keep up, you'll be fine.
